Reasoning: The paper discusses the classification of web page content, which is essential to many tasks in web information retrieval. This falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the challenges of classifying uncontrolled web content, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.DL). Finally, the paper discusses the transformation of data into an understandable structure, which is a common theme in database systems (cs.DB).
